      <title>肯尼亚的鲁托瞄准了新的雄心勃勃的目标：平衡预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/kenya-s-ruto-zeros-in-on-new-ambitious-target-a-balanced-budget</link>
